    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币短暂卷入韩国政治纷争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/bitcoin-gets-briefly-caught-up-in-south-korean-political-strife</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于韩国议会面临政治僵局，韩国总统尹锡烈宣布实施戒严，导致亚洲各交易所的价格波动大幅上升，而加密货币周二几乎没有上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/bitcoin-gets-briefly-caught-up-in-south-korean-political-strife</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 16:30:35 GMT</pubDate>
